# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Maestro .gitignore
# This repo ships the CLEAN, BLANK template. Everything tracked here
# is system + empty templates. The rules below keep your real data
# OUT of git once you start filling the brain locally.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp

# Temp / scratch / build artifacts
.tmp/
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
*.zip

# Claude Code local (machine-specific) settings
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── Personal brain data — keep templates, ignore real content ──
# Daily logs (dated files)
brain/daily/20*.md

# Client & project files (keep the template + folder mother)
brain/clients/*.md
!brain/clients/_template-client.md
!brain/clients/_clients.md
brain/projects/*.md
!brain/projects/_template-project.md
!brain/projects/_projects.md

# Development history (keep the template + folder mother in each)
brain/development/cdc/*.md
!brain/development/cdc/_template-cdc.md
!brain/development/cdc/_cdc.md
brain/development/project-feedback/*.md
!brain/development/project-feedback/_template-feedback.md
!brain/development/project-feedback/_feedback.md
brain/development/retros/*.md
!brain/development/retros/_template-retro.md
!brain/development/retros/_retros.md

# Reference notes (personal) — keep brain-conventions + the reference mother (system infrastructure)
brain/reference/*.md
!brain/reference/brain-conventions.md
!brain/reference/_reference.md

# Credentials — NEVER commit secrets (keep only the mother index + template)
brain/credentials/*.md
!brain/credentials/_credentials.md
!brain/credentials/_template-credentials.md

# Reusable tools may carry client data — ignore by default; force-add deliberately
tools/*
!tools/project_scanner.py
!tools/_tools.md

# Scanner snapshots contain project-specific data — never commit
brain/projects/*-snapshot.json

# Scanner configs contain real file paths — ignore; keep only the template
brain/projects/*-scanner-config.json
!brain/projects/_scanner-config-template.json
